---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection
    title="Magical Fauna"
    subtitle="Creatures born from Manicallus."
>

<div class="feature">

<h3>

Manicloves

</h3>

<p>

Wolf-like magical beasts native to Solmara's southern cliffs.
Created through centuries of exposure to the Eirlomanicallus beneath
the Great Lake, they possess naturally enhanced mana and crystalline
features unlike any ordinary animal.

</p>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.feature{

    max-width:900px;

    margin:auto;

    text-align:center;

}

.feature h3{

    font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

    font-size:2.5rem;

    margin-bottom:1rem;

}

.feature p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:2;

}

</style>